issue.title: [R] Change `f` to `file` in `read_parquet_file()`
issue.body:
***Note**: This issue was originally created as [ARROW-4642](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ARROW-4642). Please see the [migration documentation](https://gist.github.com/toddfarmer/12aa88361532d21902818a6044fda4c3) for further details.*

### Original Issue Description:
Change `f` to `file` in `read_parquet_file()`, otherwise you get the following error:

    Error in read_parquet_file(f) : object 'f' not found
